rows.label: qev075405_MSG0001
rows.name: I heard a fantastic ruckus over here. What is—[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev075405_MSG0002
rows.name: Can it be?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev075405_MSG0003
rows.name: T-Tolba? How are you...? How did...?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev075405_MSG0004
rows.name:
Strange Earth alien took me prisoner. I escaped when
back was turned. Good to see you, Master![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev075405_MSG0005
rows.name: No, not that! I watched you get eaten![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev075405_MSG0006
rows.name:
I'm SURE I saw it. I even swore to avenge you!
To shoulder the weight of your life and slaughter the
Ganglion wherever I found them![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev075405_MSG0007
rows.name: Dumb beast not strong enough to kill me.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev075405_MSG0008
rows.name:
Now I am even stronger. Look, Master!
Look at results of training![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev075405_MSG0009
rows.name: S-sure...[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev075405_MSG0010
rows.name:
Um...[ST:playername ]? What is going on?
What should we do?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev075405_JNK0010
rows.name: Rejoice[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev075405_SEL0011
rows.name: Celebrate the fact that Tolba is alive.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev075405_JNK0020
rows.name: Warn[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev075405_SEL0021
rows.name: Tell Gi Zang that you're sure Tolba is dead.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev075405_MSG0011
rows.name:
R-right... Right. I mean, he stands before my eyes,
does he not? There can be no doubt.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev075405_MSG0012
rows.name:
It is good to see you again, Tolba. I have watched too
many die because I could not protect them.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev075405_MSG0013
rows.name: Thank you for not being one of them.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev075405_MSG0014
rows.name: It is all thanks to training. So long, Master![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev075405_MSG0015
rows.name:
Falling for such an obvious trap. Tsk.
Wrothians really are fools.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev075405_MSG0016
rows.name: Heh heh... And now for the human.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev075405_MSG0017
rows.name:
It looks like your weapons are at least as valuable as
this sword.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev075405_MSG0018
rows.name:
I'll take them to advance the grand plan of Fortun,
as well as the glory of the Definians.
Oh, and I'll also be taking your life![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev075405_MSG0019
rows.name:
N-no, you are right. Tolba died.
I know that better than anyone.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev075405_MSG0020
rows.name: You there! Show your true self![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev075405_MSG0021
rows.name:
I can't believe I found a disguise too obvious for a
Wrothian. I mean, you guys are DENSE![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev075405_MSG0022
rows.name:
So disappointing. I was hoping to add an epilogue
to the hilarious farce I watched you play out in
Sylvalum.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev075405_MSG0023
rows.name:
I demand that you identify yourself and your purpose!
Why do you taunt me so?![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev075405_MSG0024
rows.name:
I have been tasked with gathering fine weapons.
You carried a blade that caught my eye.
...Thaaaat's pretty much it.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev075405_MSG0025
rows.name:
And your human friend there is carrying weapons at
least as tantalizing as your sword.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev075405_MSG0026
rows.name:
I'll take the lot of them to advance the grand plan of
Fortun, as well as the glory of the Definians.
Oh, and I'll also be taking your life![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev075405_MSG0027
rows.name: I am...confused.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev075405_MSG0028
rows.name:
But I suppose it DOES makes things rather simple.
I'll take the puges, friend—you take the doppelganger![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev075405_MSG0029
rows.name:
They may have set the trap, but they are the ones in
for a rude surprise![ST:wait ]
